{"tid":446421,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有excel問題想問","createTime":"2017-10-24T09:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T15:28:02.000Z","uid":2127,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2579c9979d184be91ffe68cb802def2474556adf","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T09:39:33.000Z","msg":"想問可唔可以喺同一格set if abc sum xxx 同埋if cdf sum xxx"},{"pid":"2b17d14bd285aef275d825e31315d88f9d71260d","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T09:50:14.000Z","msg":"唔係太理解你的問題，唔知下面的野o岩唔o岩你用。<br />\n<br />\n假設A1係abc, A2的數值係10, A3的數值係20, A4的數值係30。<br />\n你可以在B1打=IF(A1=&quot;abc&quot;,SUM(A2:A3),IF(A1=&quot;cdf&quot;,SUM(A2:A4),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n如果A1係abc，依條式就會將A2至A3相加，得出30。<br />\n如果A1係cdf，依條式就會將A2至A4相加，得出60。<br />\n其他情況就咩都唔會顯示。"},{"pid":"b25a423236f3ef439c2b85d39123acbad0788c5b","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"如果你想人地更易理解你的問題。<br />\n下次發問果陣你可以講清楚你的input係點，預期的output係點。<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n當A1出現abc, B1就等於Sum(A2:A3)<br />\n當A1出現cdf，B1就等於Sum(A2:A4)<br />\n<br />\n你咁得清楚其他人先答到你"},{"pid":"63d937f14fb65dcf7362c642a51ff50beb16ec1c","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係太理解你的問題，唔知下面的野o岩唔o岩你用。<br />\n<br />\n假設A1係abc, A2的數值係10, A3的數值係20, A4的數值係30。<br />\n你可以在B1打=IF(A1=&quot;abc&quot;,SUM(A2:A3),IF(A1=&quot;cdf&quot;,SUM(A2:A4),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n如果A1係abc，依條式就會將A2至A3相加，得出30。<br />\n如果A1係cdf，依條式就會將A2至A4相加，得出60。<br />\n其他情況就咩都唔會顯示。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問sumifs 係咪都可以同一格用2次架？"},{"pid":"0dd579cea19717e9f830e786339471cee4597f5c","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係太理解你的問題，唔知下面的野o岩唔o岩你用。<br />\n<br />\n假設A1係abc, A2的數值係10, A3的數值係20, A4的數值係30。<br />\n你可以在B1打=IF(A1=&quot;abc&quot;,SUM(A2:A3),IF(A1=&quot;cdf&quot;,SUM(A2:A4),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n如果A1係abc，依條式就會將A2至A3相加，得出30。<br />\n如果A1係cdf，依條式就會將A2至A4相加，得出60。<br />\n其他情況就咩都唔會顯示。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問sumifs 係咪都可以同一格用2次架？</blockquote><br />\n可以<br />\n例如=sumifs(xxxxx)+sumifs(xxxxxx)"},{"pid":"f92d7d164bfb8d83b4dd112120dbe5c2b5ca7aaa","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係太理解你的問題，唔知下面的野o岩唔o岩你用。<br />\n<br />\n假設A1係abc, A2的數值係10, A3的數值係20, A4的數值係30。<br />\n你可以在B1打=IF(A1=&quot;abc&quot;,SUM(A2:A3),IF(A1=&quot;cdf&quot;,SUM(A2:A4),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n如果A1係abc，依條式就會將A2至A3相加，得出30。<br />\n如果A1係cdf，依條式就會將A2至A4相加，得出60。<br />\n其他情況就咩都唔會顯示。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問sumifs 係咪都可以同一格用2次架？</blockquote><br />\n可以<br />\n例如=sumifs(xxxxx)+sumifs(xxxxxx)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想加個criteria，但個range唔同其他criteria，可以點解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係其他criteria 係 A1:A100 我想加嘅係A1=1"},{"pid":"dcdda2a2c3473b1278237524320f6645c212bbcc","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:17:48.000Z","msg":"咁你應該用一個if, 但係入面有多個criteria<br />\n你可以用if + and去做<br />\n例如=if(AND(A1=&quot;abc&quot;,A2=&quot;cdf&quot;),&quot;符合兩個條件&quot;,&quot;不符合兩個條件&quot;)"},{"pid":"0a63f83515e09c5093a7c9cb378442433aa5713d","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你應該用一個if, 但係入面有多個criteria<br />\n你可以用if + and去做<br />\n例如=if(AND(A1=&quot;abc&quot;,A2=&quot;cdf&quot;),&quot;符合兩個條件&quot;,&quot;不符合兩個條件&quot;)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁a1 嗰到係咪唔可以set range?<br />\n即係=if(And(a1:a10=&ldquo;abc&rdquo;,b2=&ldquo;cdf&rdquo;),sum(b11:b12),&ldquo;0&rdquo;)"},{"pid":"4523efc39eb4ee5880751e50bd68c37d304bf408","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"你應該用Countif去計算A1至10有幾多個abc<br />\n<br />\n=IF(AND(COUNTIF(A1:A10,&quot;abc&quot;)=10,B2=&quot;cdf&quot;),SUM(B11:B12),&quot;0&quot;)"},{"pid":"939874e9e17017a660d59075895b4c5e0c83305d","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/203610_79cc33824428314f08b80ec8490cdca0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F203610_79cc33824428314f08b80ec8490cdca0.jpg&h=4dc577fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打我想問如果我想喺輸入嗰個位輸入1就計價錢A，輸入2就計價錢B，應該點set？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab55eda1e44f4032d4edefda15e90926763e9eda","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/203610_79cc33824428314f08b80ec8490cdca0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F203610_79cc33824428314f08b80ec8490cdca0.jpg&h=4dc577fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打我想問如果我想喺輸入嗰個位輸入1就計價錢A，輸入2就計價錢B，應該點set？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你想咁?<br />\n=if(H1=1,sum(E:E),if(H1=2,sum(F:F),&quot;&quot;))"},{"pid":"1eac956c962d002abbba34ce377046a1d6660b6c","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/205118_3e11bad4df2de1badfc5ff2fa288cf77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F205118_3e11bad4df2de1badfc5ff2fa288cf77.jpg&h=ec292e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打少咗<br />\n仲有唔同機組型號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da53f4aad51fa1d8fb42fd16070a8b6c5d48ba9a","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/205118_3e11bad4df2de1badfc5ff2fa288cf77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F205118_3e11bad4df2de1badfc5ff2fa288cf77.jpg&h=ec292e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打少咗<br />\n仲有唔同機組型號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根據你幅圖 可以咁寫<br />\n=IF(I3=1,SUMIF(A:A,I2,E:E),IF(H3=2,SUM(A:A,I2,F:F),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n唔知係唔係你想要既結果"},{"pid":"0b248ba638fbf5aa401cb11a6d2b2c627a48ece1","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/205118_3e11bad4df2de1badfc5ff2fa288cf77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F205118_3e11bad4df2de1badfc5ff2fa288cf77.jpg&h=ec292e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打少咗<br />\n仲有唔同機組型號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根據你幅圖 可以咁寫<br />\n=IF(I3=1,SUMIF(A:A,I2,<span style=\"color: red;\">F:F</span>),IF(H3=2,SUM(A:A,I2,<span style=\"color: red;\">G:G</span>),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n唔知係唔係你想要既結果</blockquote><br />\n唔記得改返你sum果個column"},{"pid":"ea2499e08f7dc35b1b03fe9e989401fc3db72525","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/205118_3e11bad4df2de1badfc5ff2fa288cf77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F205118_3e11bad4df2de1badfc5ff2fa288cf77.jpg&h=ec292e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打少咗<br />\n仲有唔同機組型號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根據你幅圖 可以咁寫<br />\n=IF(I3=1,SUMIF(A:A,I2,<span style=\"color: red;\">F:F</span>),IF(<span style=\"color: red;\">I</span>3=2,SUM(A:A,I2,<span style=\"color: red;\">G:G</span>),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n唔知係唔係你想要既結果</blockquote><br />\n唔記得改返你sum果個column</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有唔記得改埋後面果個輸入位"},{"pid":"74bf41b591715afaf9689a24bafa5bd67935e616","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg&h=d281a012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計唔到嘅？<br />\n我想輸入2嗰陣係計G12-G19嗰個價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27032a0cb26b05f33560caa94a512098d7f56f8","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg&h=d281a012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計唔到嘅？<br />\n我想輸入2嗰陣係計G12-G19嗰個價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來我又改漏野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=IF(I3=1,SUMIF(A:A,I2,F:F),IF(I3=2,SUM<span style=\"color: red;\">IF</span>(A:A,I2,G:G),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入 &quot;1&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong> 型號 既 <strong>價錢A</strong><br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入&quot;2&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong>既型號 既 <strong>價錢B</strong><br />\n我有冇get錯?"},{"pid":"6df5ff732448e7af33a27f18e66b6af986bb2a1e","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg&h=d281a012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計唔到嘅？<br />\n我想輸入2嗰陣係計G12-G19嗰個價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來我又改漏野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=IF(I3=1,SUMIF(A:A,I2,F:F),IF(I3=2,SUM<span style=\"color: red;\">IF</span>(A:A,I2,G:G),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入 &quot;1&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong> 型號 既 <strong>價錢A</strong><br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入&quot;2&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong>既型號 既 <strong>價錢B</strong><br />\n我有冇get錯?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱呀<br />\n但原來我係想要每個零件嘅價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/214809_f1e40d4e814f5e86419ea75507152cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F214809_f1e40d4e814f5e86419ea75507152cd4.jpg&h=0712b01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係我想當機組型號A100，喺輸入嗰格入2，<br />\n零件A1，喺價錢嗰欄 會係E6*G6，<br />\n輸入1就E6*F6<br />\n<br />\n當機組型號係B100，零件A1，輸入2，價錢會係E14*G14<br />\n輸入1就 E14*F14"},{"pid":"8bac14c9b71042c114e75a9420d26392e9bed74c","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg&h=d281a012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計唔到嘅？<br />\n我想輸入2嗰陣係計G12-G19嗰個價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來我又改漏野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=IF(I3=1,SUMIF(A:A,I2,F:F),IF(I3=2,SUM<span style=\"color: red;\">IF</span>(A:A,I2,G:G),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入 &quot;1&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong> 型號 既 <strong>價錢A</strong><br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入&quot;2&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong>既型號 既 <strong>價錢B</strong><br />\n我有冇get錯?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱呀<br />\n但原來我係想要每個零件嘅價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/214809_f1e40d4e814f5e86419ea75507152cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F214809_f1e40d4e814f5e86419ea75507152cd4.jpg&h=0712b01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係我想當機組型號A100，喺輸入嗰格入2，<br />\n零件A1，喺價錢嗰欄 會係E6*G6，<br />\n輸入1就E6*F6<br />\n<br />\n當機組型號係B100，零件A1，輸入2，價錢會係E14*G14<br />\n輸入1就 E14*F14</blockquote><br />\n咁樣寫易執D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n=SUMIFS(E:E,A:A,I2,B:B,I3)*(IF(K2=1,SUMIFS(F:F,A:A,I2,B:B,I3),0)+IF(K2=2,SUMIFS(G:G,A:A,I2,B:B,I3),0))<br />\n但前題係 同一個機組同一個零件, 唔可以出現2行 <br />\n即係唔可以有2行都係A100 配 A1零件<br />\n<br />\n我而家呢條式即係<br />\n首先拎左你個型號同埋零件搵返對應既<strong>總數量</strong>先<br />\n然後再視乎你打1定2, 而去拎返<strong>價錢A</strong>/<strong>價錢B</strong>去乘返岩岩個總數量"},{"pid":"c2666f8d0fd28da19cdc19dc1a58da4dc5f3ad57","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:17:44.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n我改咗做咁先計到<br />\n=SUMIFS(E:E,A:A,$I$2,B:B,B6)*(IF($K$2=1,SUMIFS(F:F,A:A,$I$2,B:B,B6),0)+IF($K$2=2,SUMIFS(G:G,A:A,$I$2,B:B,B6),0))<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/231641_047cceb67757a1624408c1aa3f11fece.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F231641_047cceb67757a1624408c1aa3f11fece.jpg&h=805377c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我上面輸入咗B100 就唔想show A100嘅零件價錢<br />\n應該點？"},{"pid":"898545a0fe7921c1aad643e5f907540c3943095f","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打<br />\n我改咗做咁先計到<br />\n=SUMIFS(E:E,A:A,$I$2,B:B,B6)*(IF($K$2=1,SUMIFS(F:F,A:A,$I$2,B:B,B6),0)+IF($K$2=2,SUMIFS(G:G,A:A,$I$2,B:B,B6),0))<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/231641_047cceb67757a1624408c1aa3f11fece.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F231641_047cceb67757a1624408c1aa3f11fece.jpg&h=805377c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我上面輸入咗B100 就唔想show A100嘅零件價錢<br />\n應該點？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不如你講下你想做咩先<br />\n你想整個咩野表, 係邊個column show d咩數據出黎<br />\n我唔知你想要個最後結果係點"},{"pid":"e094a8f1aa8935a97036c56b281adb327c7c2380","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"個excel分上下2 parts<br />\n上面係睇價錢 更換時數 數量 等等嘅資料<br />\n<br />\n下面就係零件資料<br />\n<br />\n我想喺下面有2組價錢，a價錢同b價錢<br />\n<br />\n有n咁多組engine 同埋 每組engine都有唔同零件，但啲零件會重複嘅<br />\n<br />\n例如a engine 有  a b c d e f<br />\nB engine 有 c d e f <br />\nC engine有 a b c<br />\n<br />\n喺上面，我想整一行price list 等我睇a engine嘅價錢嗰陣，可以輕易轉到用a價錢/b價錢"},{"pid":"c637c43c1d506ece49261cda603f75af81a9961c","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"我試過用if and sumproduct sumif sumifs 嗰啲都整唔到！"},{"pid":"c57a8ce5a940b89aeff251b3535c40302b90ac28","tid":446421,"uid":107620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"放個excel出嚟<br />\n有input<br />\n有expected output (用文字整)<br />\n大約講下想點<br />\n咁會易幫你d"},{"pid":"4e5c97e64648f9240e91dc1c3fef55432bdbcb9e","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"我聽日upload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家瞓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早抖各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67226e17f21ee3ac34a9fe22ae2deb635aed6e4","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"你係「唔想show」某d內容，定係「唔想計」某d內容？"},{"pid":"95e8ec680248b6269f490670d071e7fc3fed56a2","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係「唔想show」某d內容，定係「唔想計」某d內容？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想計呀<br />\n因為上面揀咗Engine model，所以想price list只會顯示指定engine model有嘅零件嘅價錢"},{"pid":"3d37c05ff0f79bcef42d71bf24ea20ff606a6153","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個excel分上下2 parts<br />\n上面係睇價錢 更換時數 數量 等等嘅資料<br />\n<br />\n下面就係零件資料<br />\n<br />\n我想喺下面有2組價錢，a價錢同b價錢<br />\n<br />\n有n咁多組engine 同埋 每組engine都有唔同零件，但啲零件會重複嘅<br />\n<br />\n例如a engine 有  a b c d e f<br />\nB engine 有 c d e f <br />\nC engine有 a b c<br />\n<br />\n喺上面，我想整一行price list 等我睇a engine嘅價錢嗰陣，可以輕易轉到用a價錢/b價錢</blockquote><br />\n我等你upload個excel上黎再研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffb0e2671327fbb4134665156fc2c0a213151f3","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:02:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg&h=d281a012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計唔到嘅？<br />\n我想輸入2嗰陣係計G12-G19嗰個價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來我又改漏野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=IF(I3=1,SUMIF(A:A,I2,F:F),IF(I3=2,SUM<span style=\"color: red;\">IF</span>(A:A,I2,G:G),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入 &quot;1&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong> 型號 既 <strong>價錢A</strong><br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入&quot;2&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong>既型號 既 <strong>價錢B</strong><br />\n我有冇get錯?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱呀<br />\n但原來我係想要每個零件嘅價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/214809_f1e40d4e814f5e86419ea75507152cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F214809_f1e40d4e814f5e86419ea75507152cd4.jpg&h=0712b01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係我想當機組型號A100，喺輸入嗰格入2，<br />\n零件A1，喺價錢嗰欄 會係E6*G6，<br />\n輸入1就E6*F6<br />\n<br />\n當機組型號係B100，零件A1，輸入2，價錢會係E14*G14<br />\n輸入1就 E14*F14</blockquote><br />\n首先你有樣野講錯咗<br />\n你講到好似得一格要輸入咁 (K2)<br />\n但其實你有兩格要輸入 (I2同K2)<br />\n<br />\n你試下在H6入依條式睇下得唔得<br />\n=IF(A6=$I$2,IF($K$2=1,E6*F6,IF($K$2=2,E6*G6,&quot;&quot;)),&quot;&quot;)"},{"pid":"d13895ba7f0e6eaad02cb9b859386220f6891e47","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2a8ce0ba82c4fedb1ff72192b5963365e2f672","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F211031_7dda9a00b1f3ddca8789c518268186a7.jpg&h=d281a012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計唔到嘅？<br />\n我想輸入2嗰陣係計G12-G19嗰個價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來我又改漏野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=IF(I3=1,SUMIF(A:A,I2,F:F),IF(I3=2,SUM<span style=\"color: red;\">IF</span>(A:A,I2,G:G),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入 &quot;1&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong> 型號 既 <strong>價錢A</strong><br />\n當 <strong>I3</strong> 輸入&quot;2&quot; 果陣, 就計 <strong>I2</strong>既型號 既 <strong>價錢B</strong><br />\n我有冇get錯?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱呀<br />\n但原來我係想要每個零件嘅價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/214809_f1e40d4e814f5e86419ea75507152cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F214809_f1e40d4e814f5e86419ea75507152cd4.jpg&h=0712b01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係我想當機組型號A100，喺輸入嗰格入2，<br />\n零件A1，喺價錢嗰欄 會係E6*G6，<br />\n輸入1就E6*F6<br />\n<br />\n當機組型號係B100，零件A1，輸入2，價錢會係E14*G14<br />\n輸入1就 E14*F14</blockquote><br />\n首先你有樣野講錯咗<br />\n你講到好似得一格要輸入咁 (K2)<br />\n但其實你有兩格要輸入 (I2同K2)<br />\n<br />\n你試下在H6入依條式睇下得唔得<br />\n=IF(A6=$I$2,IF($K$2=1,E6*F6,IF($K$2=2,E6*G6,&quot;&quot;)),&quot;&quot;)</blockquote><br />\n岩岩沖沖下涼諗到其實可以用OFFSET幫佢做 條式簡單好多<br />\n=IF(A6=$I$2,E6*OFFSET(E6,0,$K$2),&quot;&quot;)"},{"pid":"a2167f0f7c05872d13355b1706e244ec2595cb84","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗你個file，根據我的理解<br />\n即係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在M44至M1313計數<br />\n如果B2唔等於A44，M44就唔會顯示任何數字<br />\n<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於1，M44就會計算H44*K44*M10+I44*K44<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於2，M44就會計算H44*L44*M10+I44*L44<br />\n<br />\n以上係咪你想要的野？<br />\n<br />\n在M44輸入以下公式就搞掂<br />\n=IF([@[Engine Model]]=EngineModel,IF(C10=1,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Factory Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Factory Qty]],IF(C10=2,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Company Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Company Qty]],&quot;&quot;)),&quot;&quot;)"},{"pid":"123c8560caf2c7b064ac7e87700216229210a37c","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗你個file，根據我的理解<br />\n即係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在M44至M1313計數<br />\n如果B2唔等於A44，M44就唔會顯示任何數字<br />\n<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於1，M44就會計算H44*K44*M10+I44*K44<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於2，M44就會計算H44*L44*M10+I44*L44<br />\n<br />\n以上係咪你想要的野？<br />\n<br />\n在M44輸入以下公式就搞掂<br />\n=IF([@[Engine Model]]=EngineModel,IF(C10=1,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Factory Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Factory Qty]],IF(C10=2,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Company Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Company Qty]],&quot;&quot;)),&quot;&quot;)</blockquote><br />\n我諗佢個price per interval係講緊 D11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />33"},{"pid":"77e828fededb5fca1e913d5149d100e7b41dd5e0","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗你個file，根據我的理解<br />\n即係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在M44至M1313計數<br />\n如果B2唔等於A44，M44就唔會顯示任何數字<br />\n<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於1，M44就會計算H44*K44*M10+I44*K44<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於2，M44就會計算H44*L44*M10+I44*L44<br />\n<br />\n以上係咪你想要的野？<br />\n<br />\n在M44輸入以下公式就搞掂<br />\n=IF([@[Engine Model]]=EngineModel,IF(C10=1,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Factory Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Factory Qty]],IF(C10=2,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Company Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Company Qty]],&quot;&quot;)),&quot;&quot;)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒巴打<br />\n但我係想要D9嗰個price per interval 轉<br />\n即係整個時段轉，跟返個factory interval/company interval"},{"pid":"b8a9625f28d781d1eb565defb7765472857b5780","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗你個file，根據我的理解<br />\n即係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在M44至M1313計數<br />\n如果B2唔等於A44，M44就唔會顯示任何數字<br />\n<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於1，M44就會計算H44*K44*M10+I44*K44<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於2，M44就會計算H44*L44*M10+I44*L44<br />\n<br />\n以上係咪你想要的野？<br />\n<br />\n在M44輸入以下公式就搞掂<br />\n=IF([@[Engine Model]]=EngineModel,IF(C10=1,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Factory Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Factory Qty]],IF(C10=2,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Company Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Company Qty]],&quot;&quot;)),&quot;&quot;)</blockquote><br />\n我諗佢個price per interval係講緊 D11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />33</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYes!!!"},{"pid":"d71d3e063ed9fe77ac6fb797256e37b8581eea76","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗你個file，根據我的理解<br />\n即係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在M44至M1313計數<br />\n如果B2唔等於A44，M44就唔會顯示任何數字<br />\n<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於1，M44就會計算H44*K44*M10+I44*K44<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於2，M44就會計算H44*L44*M10+I44*L44<br />\n<br />\n以上係咪你想要的野？<br />\n<br />\n在M44輸入以下公式就搞掂<br />\n=IF([@[Engine Model]]=EngineModel,IF(C10=1,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Factory Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Factory Qty]],IF(C10=2,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Company Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Company Qty]],&quot;&quot;)),&quot;&quot;)</blockquote><br />\n我諗佢個price per interval係講緊 D11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />33</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYes!!!</blockquote><br />\n係公司唔方便下載你個file<br />\n我憑印象整左個類似既表:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/105437_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F105437_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=902670af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你睇下做唔做到你要既效果"},{"pid":"b2ca2f74ccd9aa2d6d6ab2fd4b2a8f5b02ebe602","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n睇咗你個file，根據我的理解<br />\n即係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在M44至M1313計數<br />\n如果B2唔等於A44，M44就唔會顯示任何數字<br />\n<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於1，M44就會計算H44*K44*M10+I44*K44<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於2，M44就會計算H44*L44*M10+I44*L44<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n睇到眼都花<br />\n你個Excel周圍都係Factory interval, Company interval<br />\n琴晚我真係唔知你到底係想講A9至B33，D42至E1313, M42至N1313<br />\n而且你個Excel又周圍都係Price，我都唔知你講緊D11至D33，H43至H1313定係M43至M1313。<br />\n<br />\n你可唔可以好似我上面咁，直接講你想計數的範圍係邊格至邊格，你想SUM的範圍係邊格至邊格。<br />\n<br />\n而家我新的理解就係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在D11至D33計數<br />\n如果C10 = 1，D11就顯示H43:H1313的SUM （但係同時你淨係要A43:A1313當中B2的Engine Model，加上淨係要D43<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1313當中A11的Factory interval）<br />\n如果C10 = 2，D11就顯示H43:H1313的SUM （但係同時你淨係要A43:A1313當中B2的Engine Model，加上淨係要D43<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1313當中B11的Company interval）<br />\n<br />\n係咪咁呀？<br />\n<br />\n你試下下面依條得唔得？（依條式係我在無Excel的情況下打出黎，可能有少少問題）<br />\n=IF(C$10=1,sumifs(H43:H1313,A43:A1313,$B$2,D43<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1313,A11),IF(C$10=2,sumifs(H43:H1313,A43:A1313,$B$2,E43:E1313,B11),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n如果今次都唔得，麻煩你講清楚d邊格打邊格"},{"pid":"be05dac56f61e3bf9b10eab208f7e89d540eb01d","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:42:23.0