Price]]*[@[Factory Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Factory Qty]],IF(C10=2,[@[2017 Unit Price]]*[@[Company Qty]]*M$10+[@[Core deposit]]*[@[Company Qty]],&quot;&quot;)),&quot;&quot;)</blockquote><br />\n我諗佢個price per interval係講緊 D11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />33</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYes!!!</blockquote><br />\n係公司唔方便下載你個file<br />\n我憑印象整左個類似既表:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/105437_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F105437_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=902670af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你睇下做唔做到你要既效果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8855c31285e749da0861bb6cda02d9d652d93b","tid":446421,"uid":105047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n睇咗你個file，根據我的理解<br />\n即係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在M44至M1313計數<br />\n如果B2唔等於A44，M44就唔會顯示任何數字<br />\n<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於1，M44就會計算H44*K44*M10+I44*K44<br />\n如果B2等於A44，而C10等於2，M44就會計算H44*L44*M10+I44*L44<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n睇到眼都花<br />\n你個Excel周圍都係Factory interval, Company interval<br />\n琴晚我真係唔知你到底係想講A9至B33，D42至E1313, M42至N1313<br />\n而且你個Excel又周圍都係Price，我都唔知你講緊D11至D33，H43至H1313定係M43至M1313。<br />\n<br />\n你可唔可以好似我上面咁，直接講你想計數的範圍係邊格至邊格，你想SUM的範圍係邊格至邊格。<br />\n<br />\n而家我新的理解就係你有兩個位需要輸入<br />\n1. B2<br />\n2. C10<br />\n<br />\n然後你想在D11至D33計數<br />\n如果C10 = 1，D11就顯示H43:H1313的SUM （但係同時你淨係要A43:A1313當中B2的Engine Model，加上淨係要D43<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1313當中A11的Factory interval）<br />\n如果C10 = 2，D11就顯示H43:H1313的SUM （但係同時你淨係要A43:A1313當中B2的Engine Model，加上淨係要D43<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1313當中B11的Company interval）<br />\n<br />\n係咪咁呀？<br />\n<br />\n你試下下面依條得唔得？（依條式係我在無Excel的情況下打出黎，可能有少少問題）<br />\n=IF(C$10=1,sumifs(H43:H1313,A43:A1313,$B$2,D43<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1313,A11),IF(C$10=2,sumifs(H43:H1313,A43:A1313,$B$2,E43:E1313,B11),&quot;&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n如果今次都唔得，麻煩你講清楚d邊格打邊格</blockquote><br />\n我開始明佢想做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係咁:<br />\n如果C10 = 1，D11就顯示<span style=\"color: red;\">M</span>43:<span style=\"color: red;\">M</span>1313的SUM （但係同時你淨係要A43:A1313當中B2的Engine Model，加上淨係要D43: D1313當中A11的Factory interval）<br />\n如果C10 = 2，D11就顯示<span style=\"color: red;\">N</span>43:<span style=\"color: red;\">N</span>1313的SUM （但係同時你淨係要A43:A1313當中B2的Engine Model，加上淨係要<span style=\"color: red;\">E</span>43:<span style=\"color: red;\">E</span>1313當中B11的Company interval）"},{"pid":"dbc1fe1492c34483702502a2fb802c852a7861d4","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:27:44.000Z","msg":"多謝你哋2個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講到1999都明我想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用呢個就計到<br />\n=IF(C$10=1,SUMIFS(M46:M1316,A46:A1316,$B$2,D46<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1316,A13),IF(C$10=2,SUMIFS(N46:N1316,A46:A1316,$B$2,E46:E1316,B13),&quot;&quot;))"},{"pid":"17b9bd23d365e07fb42c9cd296d4baa75160929d","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"又有問題喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/110140_3d117936fe8233f3d9404676d1d4295e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F110140_3d117936fe8233f3d9404676d1d4295e.jpg&h=737abbd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/110142_a56eaec905a2d2919d4bebc7da2d85a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F110142_a56eaec905a2d2919d4bebc7da2d85a9.jpg&h=db7ae3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問有冇得set 篩選嘅時候 <br />\n唔篩走埋testing嗰格（G3)<br />\n即係無論篩咩都好 G3都要係顯示狀態"},{"pid":"11098f528c84a93973899d9583b939299b431042","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"無方法<br />\n將Testing果格擺去G1啦"},{"pid":"68fc68635ce215588fb225e2dc74464a7cead4d9","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"我又有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我想整以下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果A=1同埋B=abc，如果係就出123,唔係就出456<br />\n同一格想set 4組呢啲「如果」<br />\n<br />\n我咁寫=if(and(a=1,b=abc),123,456),if(and(a=2,b=abc),234,567)<br />\n<br />\n點解出唔到嘅"},{"pid":"640bd9f6d8439a7bef32064209027858b39c93c8","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"寫formula果陣abc要寫做&quot;abc&quot;"},{"pid":"b28527e35875c0ca658fd3ce604826a446d0644d","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫formula果陣abc要寫做&quot;abc&quot;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整咗，都係唔得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/174910_b5a364cbf84593f2d6268adea58abd83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F174910_b5a364cbf84593f2d6268adea58abd83.jpg&h=975363db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20067e5cd209c887678d98b201140a8d3e11670e","tid":446421,"uid":67069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c39686efcb4ae35656d2f152229a195cdb434d65","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"緊係出唔到啦<br />\n你條formula個logic出問題：<br />\n<br />\n而家個logic係咁的：<br />\n如果（A2 = 1 及B2 = 2）就出&quot;Yes&quot;，否則就出&quot;No&quot;。<br />\n條程式根本唔會再睇後面果個If<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，如果A2 = 1, B2 = 2，佢會出&quot;Yes&quot;<br />\n如果A2 = 1, B2 = 0，佢會出&quot;No&quot;<br />\n如果A2 = 0, B2 = 2，佢會出&quot;No&quot;<br />\n<br />\n成條程的logic睇完第一個IF就完咗"},{"pid":"e6dcb2ddb26273f5d8d84be798424998cabcae77","tid":446421,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"=IF(AND(A2=1,B2=2),&quot;Yes&quot;,IF(AND(C2=3,D2=4),&quot;Hi&quot;,&quot;Hello&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n我估你的logic應該係想咁？<br />\n舉個例，如果A2 = 1, B2 = 2，佢會出&quot;Yes&quot;<br />\n如果A2 = 1, B2 = 0，佢會出睇下一個IF，如果C2 = 3, D2 = 4，就會出&quot;Hi&quot;<br />\n如果A2 = 0, B2 = 2，佢會出睇下一個IF，如果C2 = 3, D2 = 0，就會出&quot;Hello&quot;"},{"pid":"3f0a9200a9eea3e37e6bc148370f6de790f288d1","tid":446421,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>=IF(AND(A2=1,B2=2),&quot;Yes&quot;,IF(AND(C2=3,D2=4),&quot;Hi&quot;,&quot;Hello&quot;))<br />\n<br />\n我估你的logic應該係想咁？<br />\n舉個例，如果A2 = 1, B2 = 2，佢會出&quot;Yes&quot;<br />\n如果A2 = 1, B2 = 0，佢會出睇下一個IF，如果C2 = 3, D2 = 4，就會出&quot;Hi&quot;<br />\n如果A2 = 0, B2 = 2，佢會出睇下一個IF，如果C2 = 3, D2 = 0，就會出&quot;Hello&quot;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我係想如果A2=1, B2=2 出yes，如果唔係要出no，跟住睇下一個c2同d2，true就出hi，false就出hello<br />\n<br />\n如果有下一個條件係e2同f2，true就出red，false 出blue<br />\n<br />\n應該點整"}]}